::Feline::

She waves to Firearm as her runs down the hall. "What a shame. Well, 
it looks like its just you and me Handsome. Would you mind showing me 
around? Please?" She brought her tail up and lightly brushed the tip 
of it against the back of his neck. "I'm jsut so dreadfuly thursty."
